                                    <ul>
                                        <li><strong>Estimated Budget:</strong> Initial values from CRM estimating (copied as-is)</li>
                                        <li><strong>Buyout:</strong> Pre-project adjustments made before project release/start</li>
                                        <li><strong>Current Expense:</strong> Actual expenses during project execution</li>
                                        <li><strong>Balance:</strong> Calculated as Buyout − Current Expense</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p class="mt-2"><strong>How to use adjustments:</strong></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Enter positive numbers to increase totals (e.g., 1000.00)</li>
                                        <li>Enter negative numbers to decrease totals (e.g., -500.00)</li>
                                        <li>These adjustments will be reflected in the BOM Summary Report</li>
                                        <li>The "Final Modified Price" column will show: Calculated Total + Adjustment</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </group>
